==English==
===Noun===
'''determinant''' (''plural'' '''determinants''')

#(''mathematics'') A [[scalar]] derived from a [[square matrix]] ''A'', having various uses in mathematics and defined [[recursively]] as:

<math>det\,A = \sum_{i=1}^n\;(-1)^{i+1}\;a_{1, i}\;det\,A^\prime_i</math>
:for A of dimensions ''n'' &times; ''n''; ''n'' > 1, and<br>
<math>det\,A = a_{1, 1}</math>
:for A of dimensions 1 &times; 1

where <math>A^\prime_i</math> is the matrix obtained by removing the first row and the ''i''th column from <math>A^\prime</math>.

